Several operators can work on one machine. There is therefore the need to manage machine times, but also man times.

Man and machine times are different. Example: operator 001 works from morning until lunch. Operator 003 starts the shift just before lunch. The machine, on the other hand, works from morning until evening.

The Power MES details man and machine work movements:

